{"type": "article", "id": 51582, "title": "这个书签，可以精确定位到你看的最后一个字｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-28T23:28:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48806, "name": "Yonoh"}, {"id": 8692, "name": "Poltrona Frau"}, {"id": 14845, "name": "Foster + Partners"}, {"id": 48807, "name": "Inyeop Baek"}, {"id": 48808, "name": "Lindsey Adelman"}, {"id": 48809, "name": "Piero Quintiliani"}, {"id": 48810, "name": "Ilseop Yoon"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 312, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180328225401avRuTGOtYUSLpWIg.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Pleats Chair by Ilseop Yoon</h3><p>瑞士洛桑艺术设计学院的学生 lseop Yoon，设计了一款质轻且结实的铝制座椅，波浪状的结构很醒目。受到建筑与时尚元素的影响，这款 Pleats 椅子将牢固的结构与优雅的美感结合在一起。</p><p>设计师选择铝制材料，达到质地坚硬且轻盈的特点的同时，还具有可回收的特性。为了实现优雅的美学效果，定制化的两部分模型均采用褶皱纹理图案，进而被压制成铝板作为椅子的外壳。椅子的截面从靠背连续至座位，最终成为了一个轻薄而精致的椅子外壳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225445dqDciSmn9whoK0U7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225445VYj76PuMEkvURTmw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225446vTYjKRV69xJPnyl7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225445WIjyNVkpch7ebzSa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621027\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225447KhAaHuGr4cjtLT7P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.279951\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225448nGfqehRVsD5k36uN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lastword Bookmark by Piero Quintiliani</h3><p>读书爱好者大都不缺书签，在读完一本书之前，除了用折书角的方式，都会在所读的页码处夹一张书签。但这款名为 Lastword 的书签，可以精确定位到你读的最后一个字。</p><p>设计师 Piero Quintiliani 为书签加上了金属光标，可以使用在任何形状、大小和格式的书籍上面。无论你读的是厚重的大部头，还是轻薄的杂志，这款 LastWord 书签，都能帮你节省时间，将你精确地带回你上次阅读的位置。目前，Lastword 书签有四种颜色可供选择，在意大利各大书店有售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225524HEpPX0UCDQ2r7YAF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225524zZVP7ArEhsGxluQH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225524nS67QEhkOLBxUaKD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018032822552535ItAhdX2uQ98Pz7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225526tzkEjc1J5a2KgsAQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Drop Lighting System by Lindsey Adelman </h3><p>纽约布鲁克林的设计师 Lindsey Adelman，以手工吹制的玻璃器制作的吊灯出名，她利用玻璃设计出来的吊灯看起来更像是处理过的艺术品，比如其知名的枝形造灯。</p><p>在这个名为 Drop 的新系列中，与手工吹制的迷你小灯泡搭配出现的，是定制的黄铜管，她将这个新照明系统描述为“野性的，奔放的”，黄铜灯管被盐和氨的混合物涂刷成铜绿色，像是地衣或是藻类植物的效果。这个系列可以根据客户的需求而定制，作品将会在下个月的米兰设计周上首次亮相。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225559nKSp72fshkaTHBxi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225559to8jc95Eq2ue4fih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225559sSXMZej6cbi1yPhD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225559ojxwIt6GK3Pknrzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803282255599kOyFZxBKMT8oC7D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.408313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225601YvsdnTBKJkNWy5Qr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/art/lindsey-adelman-drop-lighting-system-hand-blown-globes-brass-tubes-03-28-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>CONE by Inyeop Baek</h3><p>根据设计师 Inyeop Baek 的说法，CONE 是简化电脑鼠标的解决方案。它的滚轮舒适地放在拇指下方。虽然它呈现出与传统鼠标截然不同的外观，但锥形样式的每一个细节设计都是为了提供舒适、顺滑、简约的体验。</p><p>你可能会对这种新式垂直鼠标充满疑惑，但设计师称其完全是按照用户的手自然而然卷曲的特性而设计。除了形状之外，内置元件与传统鼠标并无区别，且与蓝牙兼容。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225640KflyogNRrXC3eHnu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225640aEgXZLuQwrPNej3s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225640lC8bt12xegRy6A0j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225641pS76jqh23FoXPb81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225641DJ5esw7Ha69QiMqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Inyeop Baek</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cove Chair by Foster + Partners for Poltrona Frau</h3><p>英国设计公司 Foster + Partners 为意大利品牌 Poltrona Frau 设计了一款名为 Cove 的椅子，适用于忙碌工作场所中需要部分隐私的人。弧形形状的靠背结构与宽大舒适的座椅结合，还内置了 USB 充电口，另有一个可作为非正式办公桌的小桌面。</p><p>这款 Cove 椅于上周在斯德哥尔摩的 2018 年国际候机楼设备展览会上亮相，Foster + Partners 团队认为其非常适合于安装在如机场休息室这样的公共场所。</p><p>Foster + Partners 工业设计总监 Mike Holland 表示，Cove 椅“用其紧凑的结构创造出一个宽敞的空间，它提供了一个僻静的空间，可以吃饭、办公或是放松。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803282258228UpTEwHDVWhMF3ai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711929\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225822UL8T7mKwPuIQcEyD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.731810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225822uTsy2EFzwjRAGcZt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225824oRGCpjakVbtTUs4M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596024\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/03/28/cove-chair-foster-partners-seating-focus-work-public-spaces/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Perpetuum Calendar by Yonoh</h3><p>Yonoh 是由 Clara del Portillo 和 Alex Selma 于 2006 年创建的多学科创意工作室。这款 Perpetuum 日历是其代表作之一。</p><p>这款尺标日历，意在提供一种全新的看日期的方式。它在设计上将时间与建筑两者的概念结合在一起，从侧面看上去像是工厂锯齿造型的屋顶。整个作品采用天然材料加上 3D 打印技术制作而成，上面有两排分别刻着月份英文缩写与日期数字，至于要如何看日期，只要把 14K 镀金、类似纸镇的这个小金属块固定在插槽中即可。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225906MrJ56aAmL9dxsvn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225906NltL48Hr21A7RY9k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.792916\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803282259066mIixKVjBUr9qgGe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225906c2qwE4jVavJfzBUu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.921250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225906fVCU2KvOPwhSZ3ry.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180328225906SWcadMYXO2ZBgGRC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909375\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Yonoh</figcaption></figure></div>"}